{"story":{"group_1":[{"bg":"bg_adv_20091.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story09","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":800400,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":402101,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"","nameRight":"塔鲁特","textLeft":"“圣女”啊……@多亏了您……","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"textLeft":"小镇从诅咒中解脱了！"},{"textLeft":"我与民众将为您鞠躬尽瘁！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":800400}],"textLeft":"直到您为法国带来@真正光明的那天！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":402101,"motion":1}],"textRight":"谢……谢谢！@城主大人！"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"chara":[{"id":810000,"pos":0,"posX":-50},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":402301,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameLeft":"丘卜","nameRight":"梅丽莎·德·维尼奥勒","textLeft":"在地理上，这座城塞一直@夹在大贵族之间左右为难。","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"textLeft":"多亏了塔鲁特，现在此地已经@完全站在了法国这边。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":402301,"motion":1}],"textRight":"是的，@日后置办补给品也方便多了！"},{"textLeft":"最终，法军保住了重要的补给线。"},{"textLeft":"塔鲁特奋不顾身的奉献精神@会让她获得越来越多的同伴。"},{"textLeft":"也会将她天生具备的因果@发展得更加庞大吧。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":402301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"textRight":"…………？"},{"chara":[{"id":402301}],"textRight":"虽然不是很明白……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":402301,"motion":300}],"textRight":"[chara:402301:effect_emotion_joy_0][se:7222_happy]但天使大人@一定说的没错吧！"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_20102.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":402201,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story02","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":402201,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"莉兹·霍克伍德","nameRight":"塔鲁特","textLeft":"你回来了，塔鲁特。","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":402101,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"textRight":"我回来了……莉兹。"},{"chara":[{"id":402101,"motion":100}],"textRight":"被邀请到不熟悉的城中，@真是把我累坏了！"},{"chara":[{"id":402201,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"今天就直接野营吧。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":402201}],"textLeft":"你可以好好休息。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":402101,"motion":1}],"textRight":"好——"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":402201,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"啊……在那之前，@必须先把灵魂宝石净化了才行。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":402201}],"textLeft":"毕竟使用了那么强的大招！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":402101,"motion":0,"mouthOpen":1}],"textRight":"啊……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":402101,"motion":201,"mouthOpen":0}],"textRight":"说得没错！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":402201,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"用悲叹之种吧。"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"chara":[{"effect":"ef_adv_09","id":402101}],"se":"7210_souljem_01","textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":402101,"motion":0}],"textRight":"谢谢你……莉兹。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":402201,"motion":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":402101}],"textLeft":"哎……塔鲁特。"},{"chara":[{"id":402201,"motion":1},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":402101}],"textLeft":"虽然我并不想考虑这些……"},{"chara":[{"id":402201}],"textLeft":"但是假如将来有一天，@我们的灵魂宝石彻底污浊……"},{"chara":[{"id":402201},{"eyeClose":1,"id":402101}],"textLeft":"真的要变成魔女的时候……"},{"chara":[{"id":402201,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"我们会有什么心愿呢？"},{"chara":[{"id":402101,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"…………"},{"chara":[{"id":402201}],"textLeft":"许愿让小镇重生的少女……"},{"chara":[{"id":402201}],"textLeft":"比起成为魔女，@更希望自己能死去……"},{"chara":[{"id":402201,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"你也会有同样的愿望吗？"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":402201}],"textLeft":"还是说……"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":402201,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"塔鲁特……"},{"chara":[{"id":402201,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"塔鲁特……@哎，你在听吗？"},{"chara":[{"id":402101}],"textRight":"唔嗯……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":402201}],"textLeft":"诶……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":402201,"motion":400}],"textLeft":"[chara:402201:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]睡着了！？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":402101}],"textRight":"[chara:402101:effect_emotion_joy_0][se:7222_happy]诶嘿嘿……@莉兹……谢谢你。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":402201,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"…………"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":402201}],"textLeft":"与其说是圣女的睡颜……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":402201,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"更像是个天真无邪的孩子呢。"},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":402101,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4021_00_05","textHome":"不管发生什么……我都要前进……"}],"nameCenter":"塔鲁特","textCenter":"我会不停前进……@无论前方有什么在等着我……","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"stop"},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":402101,"motion":201}]},{"chara":[{"id":402101}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}